(1, 'WEB DESIGN', 7, 128, 'WEB DESIGN', 1, 1, 'web_design', 1, 'burgeopnsoft-web design', 'A website is the face of the company in the virtual world of Internet. It is one of the most integral parts of a marketing campaign for any organization.', '<p><img alt="" src="http://burgeon.checkyourprojects.com/app/webroot/js/ckfinder/userfiles/files/webdesign(2).png" style="width: 288px; height: 164px;" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>A website is the face of the company in the virtual world of Internet. It is one of the most integral parts of a marketing campaign for any organization.</p>\r\n', '<section><img alt="" class="imgleftalign" src="http://burgeon.checkyourprojects.com/app/webroot/js/ckfinder/userfiles/files/web_design(1).jpg" style="width: 300px; height: 200px;" />\r\n<p>Website is the face of the business in the virtual world of Internet. It is one of the most integral parts of a marketing campaign for any organization. It is a website that allows the potential customers to have a glance of the business or service an organization offers. A well designed informative website can do wonders as it is the only medium through which an organization can reach out to the world in a short time.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>At Burgeon we help you to achieve the same. Burgeon Software acts as your consultant in the process of designing of your website and guide you at each and every step. As web design specialist, Burgeon offers:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Discussing your requirements</strong> for the website and aligning it with your business requirements.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Suggestions for RIGHT features,</strong> design and navigation requirements for your website.</li>\r\n	<li>Flexibility of <strong>multiple design concepts</strong> to make sure your get enough chances to see different design for your home page of your site before finalizing.</li>\r\n	<li>Flexibility of <strong>Unlimited revisions</strong> helps you to ensure you get what you are pleased with; no compromises.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>With our approach, we are confident that the end result will help your organizations/business to achieve the intended goals. We have tailormade website design services to suit your needs. So select from the following services based on your business needs &amp; explore our website design services.</p>\r\n\r\n<div class="gap">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</section>\r\n', NULL, 0, 1, NULL, '2013-09-13 01:19:48'),
