(27, 'Testimonials', 0, NULL, 'Testimonials', 0, 0, 'testimonials', 0, 'Testimonials', 'Testimonials', '<article>\r\n<p>Out of all the web design firms out there Burgeon Software are by far the most knowledgable and completed all of my projects on or before the scheduled time.</p>\r\n\r\n<footer>\r\n<p class="testimonial"><i>G.L. Burgess III</i><br />\r\n<a class="readmore" href="http://burgeon.checkyourprojects.com/content_manager/pages/view/27">View Site</a></p>\r\n</footer>\r\n</article>\r\n\r\n<article>\r\n<p>Professional group of indviduals with great skills. They have been helpful in regard to ideas, communication, and feedback.</p>\r\n\r\n<footer>\r\n<p class="testimonial"><i>Sheila Woodhouse</i><br />\r\n<a class="readmore" href="http://burgeon.checkyourprojects.com/content_manager/pages/view/27">View Site</a></p>\r\n</footer>\r\n</article>\r\n', '<div class="testimonial-1 t-shadow">\r\n<div class="span_12_of_12 overflow">\r\n<div class="t-img"><img alt="" src="http://burgeon.checkyourprojects.com/app/webroot/js/ckfinder/userfiles/files/jamie.jpg" /></div>\r\n\r\n<p>&quot;Once again this team never disappoints. They are very fast, great creativity, timeliness, and very great technical skill. There is nothing this team cannot do!&quot;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="span_12_of_12 overflow">\r\n<div class="t-name">Jamie<br />\r\n<small><a href="">Visit Site</a></small></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="testimonial-2 t-shadow">\r\n<div class="span_12_of_12 overflow">\r\n<p>&quot;Great Design Firm -- they were hard- working, professional, and focused on quality work. Before we started, I gave them my hand written layout and plans. They took those plans and developed a site that exactly met those plans and exceeded my expectations.<br />\r\nThank you!&quot;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="span_12_of_12 overflow">\r\n<div class="t-name">David<br />\r\n<small><a href="">Visit Site</a></small></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="testimonial-3 t-shadow">\r\n<div class="span_12_of_12 overflow">\r\n<p>&quot;Excellent work &amp; excellent quality website!! Will definitely use again on next project do not look any further!&quot;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="span_12_of_12 overflow">\r\n<div class="t-name">Sandra<br />\r\n<small><a href="">Visit Site</a></small></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="testimonial-4 t-shadow">\r\n<div class="span_12_of_12 overflow">\r\n<p><strong>&quot;Great business card design</strong> &amp; made changes I requested with- out any problem. Very professional and easy to work with.&quot;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="span_12_of_12 overflow">\r\n<div class="t-name">Sheila Woodhouse<br />\r\n<small><a href="">Visit Site</a></small></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="testimonial-5 t-shadow">\r\n<div class="span_12_of_12 overflow">\r\n<p>&quot;Professional group of indviduals with great skills. They have been helpful in regard to ideas, communication, and feedback. They have been eager to exchange ideas, and spent many hours replying to my questions to make sure I understood what they were suggesting. I would use over again.&quot;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="span_12_of_12 overflow">\r\n<div class="t-name">Sheila Woodhouse<br />\r\n<small><a href="">Visit Site</a></small></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="testimonial-6 t-shadow">\r\n<div class="span_12_of_12 overflow">\r\n<div class="t-img"><img alt="" src="http://burgeon.checkyourprojects.com/app/webroot/js/ckfinder/userfiles/files/david.jpg" /></div>\r\n\r\n<p>&quot;I&rsquo;m very impressed with the speed &amp; quality of work from the team at Burgeon with our first trial project I now trust you with more projects.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I&rsquo;m very impressed you all seem to work very long hours, I checked the time zones recently the IT people here in London are quite lazy.&quot;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="span_12_of_12 overflow">\r\n<div class="t-name">Dominic<br />\r\n<small><a href="">Visit Site</a></small></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="testimonial-7 t-shadow">\r\n<div class="span_12_of_12 overflow">\r\n<div class="t-img"><img alt="" src="http://burgeon.checkyourprojects.com/app/webroot/js/ckfinder/userfiles/files/jonson.jpg" /></div>\r\n\r\n<p>&quot;Burgeon Software, offers good value for money.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Customer service is outstanding, always available for you on chats, phones and mails.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I used Burgeon Software, to take over and correct the coding of my website from a previous developer who did a very bad job. It is not an easy job to take over and correct someone else&rsquo;s mistakes but they did it and well.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I will certainly use them again and I recommend this company to everyone&quot;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="span_12_of_12 overflow">\r\n<div class="t-name">Jason Wong<br />\r\n<small><a href="">Visit Site</a></small></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="testimonial-8 t-shadow">\r\n<div class="span_12_of_12 overflow">\r\n<p>&quot;Burgeon Software has done a fantastic job on our website. I strongly recommend using this company. Communication throughout the entire process has been excellent. Burgeon is willing to take the time to fully answer any and all questions asked. I have also been extremely impressed with the patience these guys have shown, I have had them &ldquo;update this&rdquo; and &ldquo;move that&rdquo; countless times without issue, they just keep doing the job until you are satisfied with the end result. Bottom line,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I have used 2 other companies in the past for all our websites and Burgeon has completely blown both of them out of the water. Great service, great pricing and a great product, we will definitely use them again.&quot;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="span_12_of_12 overflow">\r\n<div class="t-name">Barrett Bates<br />\r\n<small><a href="">Visit Site</a></small></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="testimonial-9 t-shadow">\r\n<div class="span_12_of_12 overflow">\r\n<div class="t-img"><img alt="" src="http://burgeon.checkyourprojects.com/app/webroot/js/ckfinder/userfiles/files/jonson.jpg" /></div>\r\n\r\n<p>&quot;Solid, thoughtful and creative work. Excellent and responsive to work with.&quot;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="span_12_of_12 overflow">\r\n<div class="t-name">Brian Cohen<br />\r\n<small><a href="">Visit Site</a></small></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="testimonial-10 t-shadow">\r\n<div class="span_12_of_12 overflow">\r\n<p>&quot;Outstanding in all respects. Product, performance and price were all outstanding, the 3 Ps for any service business, resulting in great price. I recommend Burgeon Software to anyone.&quot;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="span_12_of_12 overflow">\r\n<div class="t-name">Tahmina Watson<br />\r\n<small><a href="">Visit Site</a></small></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="testimonial-11 t-shadow">\r\n<div class="span_12_of_12 overflow">\r\n<p>&quot;Out of all the web design firms out there Burgeon Software are by far the most knowledgable and completed all of my projects on or before the scheduled time. Burgeon is now my fulltime web design firm. Out of all the web design firms out there Burgeon Software.&quot;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="span_12_of_12 overflow">\r\n<div class="t-name">G.L. Burgess III<br />\r\n<small><a href="">Visit Site</a></small></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="testimonial-12 t-shadow">\r\n<div class="span_12_of_12 overflow">\r\n<p>"Burgeon Software, were excellent from start to finish and remarkably well priced. I am really pleased with the website and feel it gives my company a great professional look. I found their communication throughout to be excellent in being both quick to reply and addressing all the points I raised - in my experience, this is a rare quality as many people just give piecemeal answers. Burgeon has been thorough, prompt, accurate and helpful in all his communication.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Thank you Burgeon Software."</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="span_12_of_12 overflow">\r\n<div class="t-name">Nick Boltan<br />\r\n<small><a href="">Visit Site</a></small></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="testimonial-13 t-shadow">\r\n<div class="span_12_of_12 overflow">\r\n<div class="t-img"><img alt="" src="http://burgeon.checkyourprojects.com/app/webroot/js/ckfinder/userfiles/files/jonson.jpg" /></div>\r\n\r\n<p>"We needed very precise modifications done to our database and Burgeon Software delivered! The timing, cost, and professionalism was great! I am going to use them again for the next set of enhancements needed for the same project. Thanks!"</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="span_12_of_12 overflow">\r\n<div class="t-name">Luc<br />\r\n<small><a href="">Visit Site</a></small></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="testimonial-14 t-shadow">\r\n<div class="span_12_of_12 overflow">\r\n<p>"Outstanding in all respects. Product, performance and price were all outstanding, the 3 Ps for any service business, resulting in great price. I recommend Burgeon Software to anyone."</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="span_12_of_12 overflow">\r\n<div class="t-name">Tahmina Watson<br />\r\n<small><a href="">Visit Site</a></small></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="testimonial-15 t-shadow">\r\n<div class="span_12_of_12 overflow">\r\n<p>"Absolutely impressed with everything from the product design to communication. Right from the start I felt like Burgeon Software, knew exactly what I wanted. And they delivered just as promised. Thank-you so much."</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="span_12_of_12 overflow">\r\n<div class="t-name">Tahmina Watson<br />\r\n<small><a href="">Visit Site</a></small></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n', NULL, 4, 1, '2013-08-28 05:41:05', '2013-09-13 01:28:11'),
